trans-unit.source: Represents a panel that supports horizontal scrolling of tabs in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon" />.
trans-unit.target: 表示一個面板，支援水平捲動 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon" /> 中的標籤。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel> provides horizontal scrolling by line for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTab> controls in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon>.
Scrolling up or down, and scrolling by page is not supported.
trans-unit.target: 不支援向上或向下捲動並逐頁捲動。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The size that the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel" /> needs to position its child elements.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel" /> 放置其子項目所需要的大小。

trans-unit.source: Positions and sizes the child elements in this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel" />.
trans-unit.target: 在這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel" /> 中，其子項目的位置和大小。

trans-unit.source: The actual size of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonTabsPanel" />.
Gets a value that indicates whether scrolling on the horizontal axis is possible.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，這個值表示是否能夠沿著水平軸捲動。
